<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id78188328-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s470aaa–9"><num value="470aaa–9">§ 470aaa–9.</num><heading> Regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">As soon as practical after <date date="2009-03-30">March 30, 2009</date>, the Secretary shall issue such regulations as are appropriate to carry out this chapter, providing opportunities for public notice and comment.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id78188329-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/111/11/tVI/s6310">Pub. L. 111–11, title VI, § 6310</ref>, <date date="2009-03-30">Mar. 30, 2009</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/123/1177">123 Stat. 1177</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
